@Node resteafaire " Still to do"

@{b}Still to do with De-Archiveur @{ub}

- Use more option of DMS. For example, more than one DMS at the same time.
 
- Saving the temporary drawer in the config file in case of someone don't
  want to have the Ram as temporary drawer.

- Choose the  AppIcon the user want to use.

- Add PGP, BASE64, UUencode, ADF if users want to have theses features.

- Support of pattern with colors other like magicWB one.

- All futurs others suggestions users want.

@EndNode

@Node Bugs " Possible Bugs "

@{b}Possible bugs with De-Archiveur @{ub}

If  De-Archiveur crash when using it, try to change in the preferences Ram
Disk:  by Ram:  and make an other try.

A  user (Didier Giron) had found this problem and found a solution even if
all  the  users  who  test  De-Archiveur had no problem with Ram Disk:  in
their config.

@EndNode

@Node Informations "Informations about NightLight Team"

@{b}Informations about the authors @{ub}

Nightlight  Team is a group of users fanatic for AMIGA and making some
programs.   We have realised somes games before.  More precision about
theses are available in the chapter @{"others products" LINK autresproductions}.

De-Archiveur  is  our first utility and our first use of BlitzBasic.
This  program  allows  us  to  discover the system programming and the
power of the BlitzBasic.

Thanks to @{b}ORION Diffusion@{ub} for having translated the BlitzBasic
2.1 in french.  This very light translation allows us to try the world
of the BlitzBasic programming.

