FONTS LISTVIEW:

Name and height for the fonts used in the menu.

FONTS BOUTONS:

Name and height for the fonts used in the buttons.

GUIDE EDITOR:

Path and name for the guide viewer.

TEXT EDITOR:

Path and name for the text viewer.

TOOL PLAYER:

Path and name for the player of modules.

TOOL PICTURE:

Path and name for the picture viewer.

PATH GUIDE FILE:

Path and name for the manual.

PATTERN:

NUMBER LINE LISTVIEW:

Number of vertical line the listview must have. 

Path and name of the pattern tou want.

PATH SAVE FILE:

Path and name for saving the settings.

SAVE SETTINGS:

